_sText:
This map was made a long time ago when I was still a bit noob'ish at hammer. (Please excuse the messiness of the map.)

I never finished since it took a long assed time to compile so I'll leave this one to you mappers/halo fans to build on this.

There's quite a bit of textures that need no drawing so you might be better off making everything no draw. The teleporters are linked to where they're supposed to be so you won't have to worry about that.
